---
title: Library
description: "Books, lectures, and papers that shaped my thinking."
layout: layouts/base
section: "library"
---

<section class="max-w-wide mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24 space-y-20 md:space-y-24">
  <!-- Page header -->
  <header class="space-y-4">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-ink">Library</h1>
    <p class="text-lead text-ink-secondary max-w-xl">
      Books, lectures, and papers that shaped how I think. Notes inside each.
    </p>
  </header>

  <!-- ================= Books ================= -->
  <section aria-labelledby="library-books" class="space-y-8">
    <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between flex-wrap gap-4">
      <h2 id="library-books" class="font-serif text-h2 text-ink">Books</h2>
      <a
        href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/161877825-jay"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        class="btn-link"
      >
        Full reading list on Goodreads
      </a>
    </div>

    <ul
      class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-8 gap-y-10 list-none m-0 p-0"
    >
      {% for book in collections.books %}
        <li>
          <a href="{{ book.url }}" class="card-media">
            <div class="card-media__media">
              {% image book.data.cover, book.data.title, "w-full aspect-[2/3] object-cover" %}
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-media__title">{{ book.data.title }}</h3>
            <p class="card-media__author">{{ book.data.author }}</p>
          </a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- ================= Lectures ================= -->
  <section aria-labelledby="library-lectures" class="space-y-8">
    <h2 id="library-lectures" class="font-serif text-h2 text-ink">Lectures</h2>
    <p class="text-body text-ink-secondary max-w-2xl">
      Lectures that completely blew me away. If you see their photo, that's me saying this person is
      pure genius.
    </p>

    <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 list-none m-0 p-0">
      {% for lecture in collections.lectures %}
        <li>
          <a href="{{ lecture.url }}" class="card-media">
            <div class="card-media__media">
              {% image lecture.data.cover, lecture.data.title, "w-full h-56 object-cover" %}
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-media__title">{{ lecture.data.title }}</h3>
            <p class="card-media__author">{{ lecture.data.author }}</p>
          </a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- ================= Papers ================= -->
  <section aria-labelledby="library-papers" class="space-y-8">
    <h2 id="library-papers" class="font-serif text-h2 text-ink">Papers</h2>
    <p class="text-body text-ink-secondary max-w-2xl">The ones I keep coming back to.</p>

    <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 list-none m-0 p-0">
      {% for paper in collections.papers %}
        <li>
          <a
            href="{{ paper.data.link or paper.url }}"
            {% if paper.data.link %}target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"{% endif %}
            class="block p-5 rounded-md bg-surface border border-border hover:border-accent transition-colors duration-base"
          >
            <h3 class="font-serif text-h4 text-ink">{{ paper.data.title }}</h3>
            {% if paper.data.author %}
              <p class="mt-2 font-sans text-ui-sm text-ink-muted">{{ paper.data.author }}</p>
            {% endif %}
          </a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </section>
</section>
